Hint
To make a selection, type the number corresponding to the option you'd like to choose.

Enjoy the CodeQuest v10.0 experience! If you need help, type "Help" for a list of available commands. To restart the game, type "Restart". To go back to the previous section, type "Back". For a hint, type "Hint".
